67.1	Michael_Pollan	Michael Pollan	Michael Pollan (born February 6, 1955) is an American author, journalist, activist, and professor of journalism at the UC Berkeley Graduate School of Journalism. A 2006 New York Times book review describes him as a "liberal foodie intellectual."	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Michael_Pollan_at_Yale_1_cropped.jpg/200px-Michael_Pollan_at_Yale_1_cropped.jpg
